WEBVTT

00:08.387 --> 00:09.755
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:09.789 --> 00:13.259
I SEE YOU ‐‐ UP THERE,
WATCHING ME.

00:13.292 --> 00:14.560
I'M A RABBI.

00:14.593 --> 00:16.429
I CAN'T KEEP MAKING
THE SAME CHOICES.

00:16.462 --> 00:17.730
THEN DON'T.

00:17.763 --> 00:18.731
I'M PREGNANT.

00:18.764 --> 00:20.399
LET'S DO THIS.
LET'S HAVE A BABY.

00:20.433 --> 00:21.801
Y‐YOU'VE GOT TO BE
KIDDING ME.

00:21.834 --> 00:23.536
I'M STILL FRESH
ON THE INSIDE.

00:23.569 --> 00:25.071
I'M GETTING A JOB.

00:25.104 --> 00:26.806
MARITOR.
IT'S SYNTHETIC POT.

00:26.839 --> 00:29.108
GOT A WHOLE RAFT OF NEW PRODUCTS
WE'RE WORKING ON

00:29.141 --> 00:30.509
WITH REAL THC.

00:30.543 --> 00:32.011
I'M CRAIG.
SILAS.

00:32.044 --> 00:33.145
Zachary: AIR!

00:33.179 --> 00:34.847
NOW HE KNOWS, ZACHARY.

00:34.880 --> 00:36.716
HELLO, MR. DOUG.

00:36.749 --> 00:38.250
HOLA, MIGUEL.
IT'S MARIA.

00:38.284 --> 00:39.485
WE'RE STARTING A CHARITY?

00:39.518 --> 00:40.920
YOUR FOUNDATION
WAS GRANTED A LICENSE

00:40.953 --> 00:43.823
TO OPERATE A FACILITY
FOR THE HOMELESS OF THIS COUNTY.

00:43.856 --> 00:46.192
YOU HAVE 48 HOURS TO MANIFEST
A LEGITIMATE FACILITY

00:46.225 --> 00:47.460
AND AVOID PROSECUTION
FOR FRAUD.

00:47.493 --> 00:48.594
[ SCOFFS ]

00:48.628 --> 00:50.029
DID ANGELA TELL YOU

00:50.062 --> 00:51.797
SHE'S BEEN ASSIGNED
TO HER FATHER'S OLD PRECINCT?

00:51.831 --> 00:53.866
WHERE ARE YOU HEADED?
I HAVE AN AGE REQUIREMENT.

00:53.899 --> 00:55.001
HAVE TO WAIT A YEAR.

00:55.034 --> 00:56.335
I GOT A GIG FOR YOU.

00:56.369 --> 00:58.738
WELCOME, SON.
YOU'VE REACHED THE INNER CIRCLE.

00:59.572 --> 01:01.340
MARK POWELL,
REGIONAL MANAGER.

01:01.374 --> 01:02.875
NEVER SEEN RESULTS
LIKE THIS.

01:02.908 --> 01:04.710
WE'VE GOT A GOLD MINE
ON OUR HANDS HERE.

