MADE OF TICKY‐TACKY ♪♪

01:18.824 --> 01:21.260
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES ON THE HILLSIDE ♪♪

01:21.294 --> 01:22.795
♪♪ BOXES ALL THE SAME ♪♪

01:22.828 --> 01:24.797
♪♪ THERE'S A GREEN ONE
AND A PINK ONE ♪♪

01:24.830 --> 01:26.799
♪♪ AND A BLUE ONE
AND A YELLOW ONE ♪♪

