01:52.058 --> 01:54.727
♪♪ AND THEY ALL LOOK
JUST THE SAME ♪♪

02:07.283 --> 02:08.784
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME?

02:08.817 --> 02:11.120
I NEED YOUR CAR KEYS.
GIVE 'EM UP.

02:11.153 --> 02:12.454
WHY?

02:12.488 --> 02:13.922
IN ONE MONTH,
YOU RACKED UP

02:13.956 --> 02:16.825
MORE SCRIPTS ON THAT LIMP
POT PILL THAN BECKY LIPSTEIN.

02:16.859 --> 02:19.695
YAY! [ CHUCKLES ]

02:19.728 --> 02:21.297
WHO'S BECKY LIPSTEIN?

02:21.330 --> 02:22.598
A GOD.

02:22.631 --> 02:24.566
YOU DID ME A FAVOR.
NOW, I'M RETURNING IT.

02:24.600 --> 02:26.568
FOR STARTERS,
YOU'RE GETTING A BETTER CAR.

02:26.602 --> 02:29.271
AND YOU'RE GONNA NEED IT.
THIS IS YOU NOW.

02:29.305 --> 02:30.906
WHAT'S ME?

02:30.940 --> 02:32.508
WESTERN NEW ENGLAND,
UPSTATE NEW YORK,

02:32.541 --> 02:33.809
PARTS OF PENNSYLVANIA.

02:33.842 --> 02:35.978
YOU'LL SPEND TWO WEEKS HERE,
TWO WEEKS OUT.

02:36.011 --> 02:37.846
THIS IS A PROMOTION ‐‐
IF YOU WANT IT.

02:37.880 --> 02:40.649
I CAN DO MORE.

02:40.683 --> 02:41.817
THAT'S A PRETTY BIG
TERRITORY.

02:41.850 --> 02:43.652
NO, I MEAN
MORE THAN MARITOR.

02:43.686 --> 02:44.887
I WANT MORE LINES ‐‐

02:44.920 --> 02:46.855
REALLY STICK IT
TO BECKY LIPSTEIN.

02:46.889 --> 02:49.291
FAIR ENOUGH, FAVORITE.

02:50.292 --> 02:53.095
AH, LIPID REGULATOR,
PROSTATE, PROSTATE,

02:53.128 --> 02:55.431
ANTIPSYCHOTIC,
DIABETES...

02:55.464 --> 02:59.301
AH. THIS IS A FUN ONE.

02:59.335 --> 03:01.303
THIS IS OUR ADDERALL.

03:01.337 --> 03:03.806
GENERIC. 2,000 SAMPLES.

03:03.839 --> 03:05.941
ADHD IS VERY HOT
RIGHT NOW.

03:05.975 --> 03:08.310
EACH ONE NEEDS TO BE
ACCOUNTED FOR BY A PHYSICIAN.

03:08.344 --> 03:10.079
HA. HOT, HOT, HOT.

03:10.112 --> 03:11.513
START LOCAL,
WORK YOUR WAY OUT.

03:11.547 --> 03:12.815
MAKE APPOINTMENTS.
MAP YOUR ROUTE.

03:12.848 --> 03:16.151
GO GET 'EM!
HA HA.

03:17.686 --> 03:18.988
[ SPITS ]

03:19.021 --> 03:21.123
WHAT ARE YOU
SO HAPPY ABOUT?

03:21.156 --> 03:22.358
I GET TO GO TO
WORK TODAY.

03:22.391 --> 03:23.559
YOU LIKE YOUR JOB?

03:23.592 --> 03:25.361
[ CHUCKLES ]
ARE YOU KIDDING?

03:27.930 --> 03:29.365
I ONLY LEFT IT
FOR TWO MINUTES.

03:29.398 --> 03:31.133
I WAS IN THE BAGGAGE CLAIM
WAITING ON MY NIECE ‐‐

03:31.166 --> 03:32.835
SIR, IF YOU LEAVE YOUR CAR
UNATTENDED IN THE RED ZONE,

03:32.868 --> 03:34.169
IT WILL GET TOWED.

03:34.203 --> 03:36.438
YOU HAVE TO PAY $300
TO THE CITY OF NEW YORK.

03:36.472 --> 03:37.706
$300?

03:37.740 --> 03:39.642
DO I LOOK LIKE
I GOT $300?!

03:39.675 --> 03:42.911
I GOT THREE KIDS!
MY EX‐WIFE MOVED TO CANADA!

03:42.945 --> 03:45.714
AND I GOT HALF A TAPEWORM
LEAKING OUT OF MY ASSHOLE!

03:45.748 --> 03:48.450
THERE A PROBLEM HERE?
HE'S BEING MEAN.

03:48.484 --> 03:49.918
GO AHEAD
AND BACK UP 10 FEET.

03:50.586 --> 03:52.454
GO ON.

03:52.488 --> 03:56.292
ONE, TWO, FIVE, NINE.
THANK YOU.

03:56.325 --> 03:58.827
THIS IS BULLSHIT!

03:58.861 --> 04:00.796
YOU LOOK CUTE
IN THAT JUMPSUIT.

04:00.829 --> 04:02.932
I THOUGHT THIS JOB
WAS GONNA BE FUN.

04:02.965 --> 04:04.266
NOW I WANT TO
KILL MYSELF.

04:05.534 --> 04:07.703
WHAT'S THIS?
JELLY MUNCHKINS.

04:07.736 --> 04:09.838
YOU'RE GOOD TO ME.
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:09.872 --> 04:12.241
[ HORN HONKS ]
LET'S GO, MULLEN!
217 IN PROGRESS.

04:12.274 --> 04:13.575
NICE! LET'S ROLL!

04:13.609 --> 04:15.311
MAN, I WANT A 217.

04:15.344 --> 04:16.512
HANG IN THERE.

04:16.545 --> 04:18.948
PLEASE BE CAREFUL.
BYE.

04:18.981 --> 04:21.150
THAT'S RIGHT. WAVE.

04:21.183 --> 04:22.418
WAVE LIKE A BITCH.

04:24.153 --> 04:26.855
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

04:26.889 --> 04:29.158
I'LL BE IN
YOUR NECK OF THE WOODS...

04:30.326 --> 04:31.560
...NEXT THURSDAY.

04:31.594 --> 04:33.762
IS THAT GOOD?

04:33.796 --> 04:36.899
GREAT. LOVE NEW HAMPSHIRE.
BYE.

04:36.932 --> 04:39.168
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

04:39.201 --> 04:42.104
I'M HAVING A PRIVATE SNACK.
AWAY FROM PEOPLE.

04:42.137 --> 04:44.840
[ CRUNCHING ]
YOUR TUB IS BEAUTIFUL.

04:44.873 --> 04:45.941
MINE'S
SHAPED LIKE A COFFIN.

04:45.975 --> 04:48.410
SHOULDN'T YOU BE
NOT HERE?

04:48.444 --> 04:49.845
IS THAT PâTé?

04:49.878 --> 04:51.547
CLOSE THE DOOR.

04:51.580 --> 04:54.016
MMM. YES!

04:54.049 --> 04:55.150
FOIE GRAS.

04:55.184 --> 04:58.253
BOUGHT A CASE. SUPER DEAL.
FUCK THOSE FAT GEESE.

04:58.287 --> 05:00.322
YOU CAN'T EAT THAT.
YOU'RE PREGNANT.

05:00.356 --> 05:01.523
IS ‐‐ IS THAT WINE?

05:01.557 --> 05:05.094
[ SIGHS ]

05:05.127 --> 05:07.463
NOT PREGNANT.

05:08.731 --> 05:09.932
MENOPAUSE.

05:09.965 --> 05:13.936
SADISTICALLY‐EARLY
MENOPAUSE.

05:13.969 --> 05:17.806
MY NEW HORMONAL STEW
SPAT OUT A FALSE POSITIVE.

05:17.840 --> 05:21.810
I SAW AN OB/GYN.
I'M OLD.

05:23.612 --> 05:25.381
I'M AN OLD MARE
WHO CAN'T HAVE BABIES.

05:25.414 --> 05:29.785
I'M OUR MOM WITH A BAG
OF FROZEN GRAPES ON HER FACE.

05:29.818 --> 05:30.919
[ SCOFFS ]

05:30.953 --> 05:33.555
WHICH MEANS YOU'RE NEXT.
YOU'RE NEXT.

05:33.589 --> 05:35.724
YOU JUST FIND OUT
OR WHEN WAS ALL THIS?

05:35.758 --> 05:37.826
YEAH.
LIKE THREE WEEKS AGO.

05:37.860 --> 05:40.963
THREE WEEKS?
JESUS, JILL.

05:40.996 --> 05:42.031
WHAT?!

05:42.064 --> 05:44.166
I LIKE SECRETS.
THEY'RE ALL I HAVE.

05:44.199 --> 05:45.167
DRINK WITH ME.

05:45.200 --> 05:47.970
UH, ANDY.
YOU NEED TO TELL HIM.

05:48.003 --> 05:50.105
UNH‐UNH.
NOT YOUR CALL.

05:50.139 --> 05:52.041
YES. MY CALL.

05:52.074 --> 05:54.109
MY WINE, MY BATHROOM,
MY BROTHER‐IN‐LAW.

05:54.143 --> 05:55.244
MY CALL.

05:55.277 --> 05:58.781
THERE ARE HOLES IN MY LIFE.
MANY HOLES.

05:58.814 --> 06:00.649
I'VE, YOU KNOW,
TRIED TO FILL THEM

06:00.683 --> 06:04.386
WITH COUPONS
AND DICK AND BABIES,

06:04.420 --> 06:06.922
BUT THERE
ARE SO MANY HOLES

06:06.956 --> 06:09.625
THAT NOW I, MYSELF,
HAVE BECOME A HOLE.

06:09.658 --> 06:14.964
HOLLOW...FALLOW...
EMPTY.

06:16.432 --> 06:19.068
EXCEPT FOR ANDY.

06:19.101 --> 06:22.972
I LIKE HIM.
YOU KNOW HE'LL LEAVE ME.

06:23.005 --> 06:27.109
I...
HE'LL UNDERSTAND.

06:27.142 --> 06:28.477
YOU DON'T EVEN
WANT US TOGETHER.

06:28.510 --> 06:29.712
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

06:29.745 --> 06:32.247
ANDY? HAVE YOU
LISTENED TO HIM LATELY?

06:32.281 --> 06:35.250
NOT ONE FRACTURED FAIRY TALE
FROM THE GOOD OLD DAYS.

06:35.284 --> 06:39.788
NOT ONE "REMEMBER THAT TIME
I TRIPPED ON A LEPRECHAUN

06:39.822 --> 06:41.223
AND BLAH, BLAH."

06:41.257 --> 06:44.293
YOU MAKE HIM LOOK FORWARD.
DON'T "F" THIS UP.

06:44.326 --> 06:47.696
I WILL TELL HIM...

06:47.730 --> 06:48.797
WHEN I TELL HIM.

06:48.831 --> 06:51.000
OR I CAN TELL HIM.
NO!

06:57.606 --> 07:00.576
♪♪ OH, OH ♪♪

07:00.609 --> 07:03.212
[ MUZAK PLAYS ]

07:08.017 --> 07:10.719
I'M SORRY. HE'S LATE.

07:10.753 --> 07:13.856
WOULD YOU LIKE HIS LATTE?
HE NEVER DRINKS IT.

07:13.889 --> 07:15.591
OH, NO. THANK YOU.
I'M EARLY.

07:15.624 --> 07:18.227
WHAT YOU PEDDLIN'?

07:18.260 --> 07:21.430
UH, ADHD.

07:21.463 --> 07:22.564
ADDERALL. GENERIC.

07:22.598 --> 07:25.534
AH. THE SPEEDY STUFF.

07:25.567 --> 07:28.170
MY GRANDSON
GOES TO CONN COLLEGE.

07:28.203 --> 07:31.407
UP IN NEW LONDON.

07:33.609 --> 07:36.312
I COULD UNLOAD THOSE
FOR 10 BUCKS A PILL.

07:36.345 --> 07:38.514
ON CAMPUS.

07:38.547 --> 07:39.782
$20 DURING RUSH WEEK.

07:39.815 --> 07:43.052
KEEPS THE PARTY GOIN'.
YOU IN?

07:43.085 --> 07:44.586
HA.

07:44.620 --> 07:46.055
OKAY.

07:46.088 --> 07:47.723
NO JOKE.

07:47.756 --> 07:49.892
30%.
2,000 EXTRA BONES A MONTH.

07:49.925 --> 07:51.760
I'LL ACCOUNT
FOR EVERYTHING.

07:51.794 --> 07:53.562
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
LIFT A FINGER.

07:53.596 --> 07:54.964
I'M JOAN.

07:54.997 --> 07:57.032
NANCY.

07:57.066 --> 07:59.902
SO...
DO WE HAVE A DEAL?

07:59.935 --> 08:06.642
WHY WOULD YOU PEG ME FOR
SOMEONE WHO, YOU KNOW, WOULD ‐‐

08:06.675 --> 08:09.678
DO I JUST RADIATE
CRIMINAL VIBES, OR...?

08:09.712 --> 08:11.313
PRISON TATTOO
ON YOUR SHOULDER.

08:11.347 --> 08:13.082
RIGHT.

08:13.115 --> 08:14.650
THAT AND
NOBODY'S EVER SAID NO.

08:14.683 --> 08:16.452
[ DOOR OPENS ]

08:16.485 --> 08:21.390
DR. FRIEDMAN
CAN SEE YOU NOW.

08:21.423 --> 08:22.992
THINK ABOUT IT.

08:25.060 --> 08:27.830
HEY. COME HERE.
LOOK AT THIS.

08:27.863 --> 08:30.299
SEE THOSE LITTLE WHITE HAIRS
ON THE STEM?

08:30.332 --> 08:31.800
YEAH.YEAH.

08:31.834 --> 08:34.370
IF YOU BURY THOSE UNDERGROUND,
THAT BECOMES THE ROOTS.

08:34.403 --> 08:36.639
YOU COULD BURY THE WHOLE PLANT
IF WE WERE OUTSIDE.

08:36.672 --> 08:37.973
WOW.WOW.

08:38.007 --> 08:40.209
WHOA. LOOK AT THIS!
THESE GUYS ARE READY TO EAT.

08:40.242 --> 08:41.343
[ CRUNCH ] MMM.

08:41.377 --> 08:44.446
[ Muffled ] OH, MY GOD.
THAT'S GOOD. HERE.

08:44.480 --> 08:46.115
I DON'T LIKE TOMATOES.

08:46.148 --> 08:48.217
YEAH, BUT THEY'RE NOT JUST
REGULAR TOMATOES.

08:48.250 --> 08:50.286
THOSE ARE SHAYLA
AND TAYLOR TOMATOES.

08:50.319 --> 08:51.954
YOU GREW 'EM, RIGHT?

08:51.987 --> 08:53.856
[ TOMATOES CRUNCH ]

08:53.889 --> 08:55.557
Both: [ Muffled ]
MMM. AMAZING!

08:55.591 --> 08:58.727
[ CHUCKLES ] RIGHT?
JILL, WANT TO TRY?

09:00.095 --> 09:01.330
UM...

09:01.363 --> 09:03.032
GIRLS,
GO INSIDE THE HOUSE.

09:08.604 --> 09:10.005
[ SNIFFS ]

09:10.039 --> 09:12.541
WHAT KIND OF STANK STRAIN
YOU BREWIN' OVER THERE?

09:12.574 --> 09:13.776
SMELLS LIKE ASS.

09:13.809 --> 09:16.445
YOU WANT TO SEE
HOW OURS MATCH UP?

09:16.478 --> 09:17.713
I COULD THROW DOWN.

09:17.746 --> 09:19.715
SO LET'S THROW DOWN.

09:19.748 --> 09:21.050
BLOW SMOKE
AT CAGED RACCOONS

09:21.083 --> 09:22.785
AND SEE WHICH ONE
EATS THE MOST CHEETOS

09:22.818 --> 09:24.053
IN A SET AMOUNT OF TIME?

09:24.086 --> 09:25.955
BRING IT ON.

09:25.988 --> 09:27.222
[ RACCOON SQUEAKS ]

09:27.256 --> 09:29.925
[ COUGHS ]
WHAT ARE YOU UP TO? I'M ON 34.

09:29.959 --> 09:31.293
I HAVE NO IDEA.
I LOST COUNT.

09:31.327 --> 09:32.428
62.

09:32.461 --> 09:34.563
62? BULLSHIT.

09:34.597 --> 09:37.266
WHO'S GOT THE MUNCHIES?

09:37.299 --> 09:39.702
YEAH!
63! 63!

09:39.735 --> 09:41.170
THERE'S NO WAY.
FUCK YOUR RACCOONY FACE!

09:41.203 --> 09:43.806
GENTLEMEN. NOPE.
WE DON'T DO THAT.

09:43.839 --> 09:46.575
WE DON'T ROLL UP
$15 MILLION OF R&D

09:46.609 --> 09:48.277
AND SMOKE IT.

09:48.310 --> 09:49.979
FUCK, GUYS.

09:50.012 --> 09:51.213
THESE CAGES HAD LABELS.

09:51.246 --> 09:53.649
ONE OF THEM
HAS TESTICULAR CANCER.

09:53.682 --> 09:55.651
NOW I DON'T KNOW WHICH.

09:55.684 --> 09:57.119
PETA ALREADY
WANTS THIS PLACE TORCHED.

09:57.152 --> 09:59.355
[ RACCOON WARBLES ]
THAT SAID, WHO WON?

10:01.323 --> 10:03.392
[ SIGHS ]
INTERESTING.

10:03.425 --> 10:04.927
SHOW ME YOUR PLANT.

10:06.595 --> 10:07.796
[ CRUNCH ]

10:14.270 --> 10:19.108
Nancy:
PROVIDENCE TO FALL RIVER.

10:19.141 --> 10:23.979
FALL RIVER TO QUINCY.

10:24.013 --> 10:26.815
QUINCY TO NASHUA.

10:26.849 --> 10:28.651
HEY, STEVIE,

10:28.684 --> 10:32.321
WHAT'S THE CAPITAL
OF NEW YORK?

10:32.354 --> 10:33.989
BAGELS?

10:34.023 --> 10:36.125
THAT'S NOT A ‐‐

10:36.158 --> 10:39.295
WHAT ABOUT, UH,
PENNSYLVANIA?

10:39.328 --> 10:40.229
PITTSBURGH?

10:40.262 --> 10:43.432
WHO TAUGHT YOU THAT?
SHANE.

10:43.465 --> 10:46.569
HEY, STEVIE, WHAT'S THE CAPITAL
OF CONNECTICUT?

10:46.602 --> 10:47.670
I DON'T KNOW.

10:47.703 --> 10:49.772
SURE YOU DO.
THINK HARD. COME ON.

10:49.805 --> 10:51.106
PRISON?

10:51.140 --> 10:55.978
WHAT? THAT'S ‐‐
THAT'S NOT A CITY, SILLY.

10:56.011 --> 10:57.513
YOU LIVED THERE.

11:00.883 --> 11:02.718
HELLO, THERE,
BEAUTIFUL.

11:02.751 --> 11:06.121
MIND IF I SIT?
THANK YOU. THANKS.

11:06.155 --> 11:08.257
ME ‐‐ DOUG WILSON.

11:08.290 --> 11:11.060
YOU ‐‐ HOMELESS LADY
ON MILK CRATE.

11:11.093 --> 11:15.931
I COME FROM OLD SANDWICH,
LAND OF GREAT WEALTH.

11:15.965 --> 11:19.802
IT IS A PLACE
THREE DAYS' WALK FROM HERE.

11:19.835 --> 11:22.471
OR 10‐MINUTE CAR RIDE.

11:22.504 --> 11:25.207
IT IS THERE
WHERE I RUN MY SHELTER

11:25.241 --> 11:27.810
FOR THOSE
THAT DO NOT HAVE ROOF.

11:27.843 --> 11:30.980
YOU UNDERSTAND "ROOF"?

11:31.013 --> 11:33.849
THESE ARE PHOTOGRAPHS
OF MY ROOF SHELTER.

11:33.883 --> 11:36.986
WITHOUT TENANTS
LIKE YOURSELF,

11:37.019 --> 11:39.321
THE STATE INSPECTOR
WILL SHUT US DOWN.

11:39.355 --> 11:40.256
BOO!

11:40.289 --> 11:41.657
THAT'S WHY WE NEED YOU.

11:41.690 --> 11:44.693
HOW'S THAT SOUND?
DOES THAT SOUND PRETTY GOOD?

11:44.727 --> 11:46.161
[ GASPS ]

11:46.195 --> 11:47.563
OHH!

11:47.596 --> 11:49.131
OH, MY GOD!

11:54.069 --> 11:55.838
THREE WEEKS?!

11:55.871 --> 11:58.641
YOU MADE ME
THINK OF NAMES.

11:58.674 --> 12:02.311
YOU MADE ME GO SHOPPING
FOR YOUR VITAMINS.

12:02.344 --> 12:03.479
I GOT A JOB.

12:03.512 --> 12:06.081
I AMAZONED
"GO THE FUCK TO SLEEP."

12:06.115 --> 12:07.950
I CALLED AUDRA.

12:07.983 --> 12:09.084
WHO'S AUDRA?

12:09.118 --> 12:10.719
MY EX.
SHE'S AN OB/GYN.

12:10.753 --> 12:12.655
I WANTED TO KNOW
WHEN THEY KICK.

12:12.688 --> 12:13.923
14 WEEKS!

12:13.956 --> 12:16.091
ASK ME! YOU DON'T
HAVE TO CALL YOUR EX!

12:16.125 --> 12:17.359
YOU WEREN'T HERE!

12:17.393 --> 12:19.361
YOU WERE OFF SOMEWHERE
NOT BEING PREGNANT.

12:19.395 --> 12:21.163
GETTING DRUNK
OFF YOUR FIBS!

12:21.197 --> 12:22.498
NOT THAT IT MATTERS,
ANYWAY.

12:22.531 --> 12:24.033
SHE DIDN'T PICK UP.
I LEFT A VOICEMAIL.

12:24.066 --> 12:26.902
BUT I PUT IT OUT
INTO THE WORLD!

12:26.936 --> 12:29.171
I TOLD PEOPLE!

12:29.205 --> 12:31.106
UGH!

12:31.140 --> 12:32.575
I HAD A MOLD TAKEN.

12:32.608 --> 12:33.709
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

12:33.742 --> 12:35.110
FOR PROSTHETIC TOES.

12:35.144 --> 12:36.645
WHY DO YOU NEED FAKE TOES?

12:36.679 --> 12:41.250
TO HAVE A WHOLE FOOT!
TO NOT BE A FREAK FATHER.

12:41.283 --> 12:43.986
SO WE COULD ENJOY A BEACH.

12:44.019 --> 12:45.854
SOCKS WITH SANDALS?

12:45.888 --> 12:48.390
LAME! LAME, DAD! LAME!

12:48.424 --> 12:50.926
IT'S MENOPAUSE, ANDY.
IT'S NOT A CHOICE.

12:50.960 --> 12:53.662
I GOT TO GO TO WORK.
LITTLE JEWS NEED ME.

12:53.696 --> 12:54.763
YOU LIED.

12:54.797 --> 12:56.031
DO NOT LEAVE THE ROOM.

12:56.065 --> 12:58.300
YOU NEVER,
NEVER LEAVE THE ROOM.

13:00.102 --> 13:01.804
BOTH MY SONS WORK.

13:01.837 --> 13:04.206
MY SISTER
AND MY BEST FRIEND

13:04.240 --> 13:09.078
ARE HAVING A SEXY CRYFEST
BEHIND CLOSED DOORS.

13:09.111 --> 13:15.684
AND YOUR LAST WORDS OF ADVICE ‐‐
WELL, THEY REALLY WORKED.

13:15.718 --> 13:17.353
IT'S NICE
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

13:17.386 --> 13:21.991
EVERYWHERE I LOOK,
I SEE TEMPTATION.

13:22.024 --> 13:23.359
ME, TOO.

13:24.560 --> 13:26.228
I MEAN, WE ALL DO.

13:26.262 --> 13:27.763
WHAT DO YOU DO ABOUT IT?

13:27.796 --> 13:33.369
YOU SEE, THE TALMUD ‐‐ IT'S LIKE
OUR SUPPLEMENT BIBLE ‐‐

13:33.402 --> 13:37.239
BELIEVES THAT GOD PUTS EVERY MAN
AT EQUAL DISTANCE

13:37.273 --> 13:39.375
FROM YETZER HATOV,
WHICH IS GOOD,

13:39.408 --> 13:41.710
AND YETZER HARA,
WHICH IS EVIL.

13:41.744 --> 13:43.979
YESTER‐‐
YETZER HARA.

13:44.013 --> 13:45.381
BUT IT'S NOT EVIL,
PER SE.

13:45.414 --> 13:47.850
IT DESCRIBES
THE INCLINATION WE ALL HAVE

13:47.883 --> 13:49.652
TO PERVERT
OUR MOST BASIC NEEDS.

13:49.685 --> 13:50.920
SO,
FOOD BECOMES GLUTTONY.

13:50.953 --> 13:53.055
MONEY, GREED.

13:53.088 --> 13:55.424
LOVE, LUST.

13:57.226 --> 13:58.928
YOU KNOW,
THAT NIGHT BY THE POOL,

13:58.961 --> 14:00.496
I REALLY
WANTED TO KISS YOU.

14:00.529 --> 14:02.965
SO WHY DIDN'T YOU?

14:02.998 --> 14:04.733
I DON'T KNOW.

14:06.135 --> 14:09.104
I MEAN...
I MADE A CHOICE.

14:09.138 --> 14:10.839
YEAH, WELL,
I DIDN'T COME HERE

14:10.873 --> 14:12.441
TO TALK ABOUT
THAT NIGHT BY THE POOL.

14:12.474 --> 14:15.678
OH. THEN WHAT
ARE WE TALKING ABOUT?

14:15.711 --> 14:17.813
I AM STRUGGLING WITH

14:17.846 --> 14:20.449
A QUESTIONABLE
BUSINESS DECISION.

14:20.482 --> 14:23.852
OH!

14:23.886 --> 14:25.854
IT'S NO DIFFERENT.
[ SIGHS ] NO?

14:25.888 --> 14:27.189
NO.

14:27.223 --> 14:30.226
GOD PUTS EVERYONE FIVE MILES
FROM YETZER HARA

14:30.259 --> 14:31.227
AND FIVE MILES FROM
YETZER HATOV.

14:31.260 --> 14:32.595
BUT HE DOESN'T NUDGE.

14:32.628 --> 14:35.297
HE WANTS US ALL
TO MAKE THE RIGHT CHOICE.

14:35.331 --> 14:38.000
HE GIVES US ALL A CHANCE
AT PERFECTION.

14:39.235 --> 14:43.672
ISN'T PERFECTION...

14:43.706 --> 14:44.940
SUBJECTIVE?

14:44.974 --> 14:48.010
SURE.

14:52.815 --> 14:54.416
[ BUTTONS POPPING ]

14:59.655 --> 15:01.724
YOU'RE A WOMAN, MANUEL.
SHE'LL LISTEN TO YOU.

15:01.757 --> 15:03.225
IT'S MARIA.

15:03.259 --> 15:05.094
SHE NEEDS OUR HELP.
YOU'RE DOING THE LORD'S WORK.

15:05.127 --> 15:06.795
WITHOUT THIS CHARITY,
I AM BROKE.

15:06.829 --> 15:08.931
NO MONEY. NO SPACE SUIT.
WE NEED HER.

15:08.964 --> 15:10.232
[ GASPS ]
OKAY. I TRY.

15:10.266 --> 15:14.570
HOLA.
MY FRIEND IS A GOOD MAN.

15:14.603 --> 15:15.671
HE WILL HELP YOU, YES?

15:15.704 --> 15:19.475
AAH! AY DIOS MíO!

15:19.508 --> 15:22.077
OKAY, ASK HER AGAIN.
ASK HER NICELY.
NO!

15:22.111 --> 15:23.078
ASK HER NICELY!
NO! [ SOBS ]

15:23.112 --> 15:24.446
JUST ONE MORE TIME.

15:24.480 --> 15:26.549
ALL RIGHT. COME ON.
WALK IT OFF. WALK IT OFF.

15:26.582 --> 15:27.650
[ SOBS ]

15:27.683 --> 15:28.951
