WHERE?

15:28.984 --> 15:31.820
SEX! WE CAN HAVE SEX.
WE CAN HAVE SO MUCH SEX.

15:31.854 --> 15:34.256
SEX WITHOUT CONDOMS.
SEX WITH WILD ABANDON.

15:34.290 --> 15:37.092
PLUS, NO MORE BLOATING,
NO MORE CRAMPING,

15:37.126 --> 15:39.228
AND ACCORDING TO ONE
COMMENTER ON ivillage.com,

15:39.261 --> 15:41.764
I'LL RECEIVE A RAPID INFLUX
OF ELEGANCE AND GRACE.

15:41.797 --> 15:44.033
CAN'T THEY PUT EGGS
BACK INSIDE YOU?

15:44.066 --> 15:45.467
WHY DON'T WE USE NANCY'S?

15:46.936 --> 15:50.506
WHAT? SHE'S YOUR SISTER.
IS THAT WEIRD?

15:50.539 --> 15:51.774
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

15:51.807 --> 15:53.309
CRYING BABIES
OR SCREAMING ORGASMS?

15:57.079 --> 15:59.281
LET'S ADOPT.

16:01.317 --> 16:03.152
HMM?

16:05.120 --> 16:08.557
[ MUZAK PLAYS ]

16:08.591 --> 16:12.194
HI. NANCY.
FROM EARLIER.

16:12.228 --> 16:16.799
