ONE OF THOSE GYMNASTS.

16:40.022 --> 16:42.124
[ MOANS ]

16:42.157 --> 16:43.425
WHAT ABOUT RUSSIA?

16:43.459 --> 16:45.561
OH! RUSSIA.

16:45.594 --> 16:47.363
RUSSIANS BLEND WELL.

16:47.396 --> 16:48.797
